OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest told 'there's so
OL,4,Cmuch we still don't know' about death
OL,6,FThe inquest into the death of Noah
OL,7,FDonohoe has heard that an unexplained
OL,8,Ftrip he took the night before his
OL,9,Fdisappearance, could be typical
OL,10,Fbehaviour for children who are
OL,11,Fcriminally exploited.
OL,13,FA group of psychologists and
OL,14,Fpsychiatrists, who examined the
OL,15,Fcircumstances surrounding the
OL,16,Fschoolboy's disappearance and death in
OL,17,FJune 2020, gave evidence on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
