CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1781039474
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest told 'there's so
OL,4,Cmuch we still don't know' about death
OL,6,FJurors at Belfast Coroner's Court
OL,7,Fheard there are still too many
OL,8,Funknowns to explain Noah's behaviour
OL,9,Fbefore his death, however, they have
OL,10,Fexcluded possible explanations such as
OL,11,Fillegal substance use and psychosis.
OL,13,FThe 14-year-old had been planning to
OL,14,Fmeet with school friends at Cavehill
OL,15,Fin Belfast after setting out on his
OL,16,Fbike on Sunday, June 21 2020.
OL,18,FHe was captured on CCTV cycling
OL,19,Fthrough the city centre and then
OL,20,Ftowards the north of the city.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1781039474
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest told 'there's so
OL,4,Cmuch we still don't know' about death
OL,6,FIn the final clip, the last footage of
OL,7,FNoah before he disappeared, he is seen
OL,8,Friding the bike naked.
OL,10,FHis naked body was found in an
OL,11,Funderground water tunnel on June 27,
OL,12,Fsix days after he left home.
OL,14,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,15,Flikely cause of death was drowning.
OL,17,FOn Tuesday, psychologist Dr Louise
OL,18,FBowers told the court: "It feels like
OL,19,Fthere is so much that we still don't
OL,20,Fknow.
OL,26,@zD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1781039474
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest told 'there's so
OL,4,Cmuch we still don't know' about death
OL,6,F"As psychologists we like to have
OL,7,Fanswers and we like to have everything
OL,8,Ftied up with a bow on top and this is
OL,9,Fone of those cases where it just isn't
OL,10,Flike that, we almost know less than we
OL,11,Fdo know."
OL,13,FDr Bowers told the court that she only
OL,14,Ffound out recently that Noah had left
OL,15,Fhis house the night before he
OL,16,Fdisappeared, adding: "That appears to
OL,17,Fhave been a little bit overlooked."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@IO]xD@VOUyD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1781039474
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest told 'there's so
OL,4,Cmuch we still don't know' about death
OL,6,FShe went on: "Understanding where he
OL,7,Fwent, whether he met anybody, if he
OL,8,Fdid meet anybody, what conversations
OL,9,Ftook place and what happened to his
OL,10,Fflip flops and headphones, from a
OL,11,Fpsychological perspective and a
OL,12,Frelational perspective appear quite
OL,13,Fimportant to me.
OL,15,F"But I accept that we simply don't
OL,16,Fknow and it may be that we're unlikely
OL,17,Fto ever know the answers to those
OL,18,Fquestions, so I have to live with that
OL,19,Funcertainty.
OL,26,@nD@NOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1781039474
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest told 'there's so
OL,4,Cmuch we still don't know' about death
OL,6,F"From a psychological perspective
OL,7,Fhaving those answers I think would
OL,8,Fhave helped me a great deal in trying
OL,9,Fto understand what happened to Noah."
OL,11,FShe told of feeling a "sadness" that
OL,12,Fshe was not able to assist in getting
OL,13,Fcloser to the answers.
OL,15,FPsychiatrist Dr Seena Fazel told
OL,16,Fjurors that the experts have excluded
OL,17,Fsome possible explanations such as a
OL,18,Fhead injury, psychosis, illegal
OL,19,Fsubstance use and other mental
OL,20,Fdisorders.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@eO]sD@WOUsD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1781039474
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest told 'there's so
OL,4,Cmuch we still don't know' about death
OL,6,FHe added: "At the same time we're not
OL,7,Fable to go further and provide a
OL,8,Fdefined explanation."
OL,10,FDr Girish Vaidya, a psychiatrist, said
OL,11,FNoah's behaviour "does defy an
OL,12,Fexplanation within the bounds of
OL,13,Fmental health as we know it".
OL,26,@nD@KOUpD@UO]sD@ROUuD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1781039474
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest told 'there's so
OL,4,Cmuch we still don't know' about death
OL,6,F"There are a lot of unknowns, and
OL,7,Fthose unknowns add to the difficulty
OL,8,Fin coming to a conclusion but from
OL,9,Fwhat we know so far, from a mental
OL,10,Fhealth point of view, there isn't any
OL,11,Fevidence to suggest that it was a
OL,12,Fmental health issue that caused him to
OL,13,Fbehave the way that he did."
OL,15,FPsychiatrist Dr Richard Church said
OL,16,Fthere was an "absence of any clear
OL,17,Fmental disorder that might help
OL,18,Fexplain his disappearance and tragic
OL,19,Fdeath".
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@\O]xD@NOU{D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
